stalone tray 0.3 highlights:
 - bugfixes/stability improvements
 - new bugs
 - root transparency support

stalone tray 0.2 highlights:
 - native kde tray icons support
 - support for unusially-sized icons
 - support for icons that change their sizez
 - rc file (copy stralonetrayrc.sample to ~/.stalonetrayrc)
 - debug mode is on by default
